description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a change in career? Do you want a role that allows you the flexibility to work around your personal commitments? Do you want to work for an “outstanding” Trust?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is initially on an adhoc basis including our 16:30 -19:30 shifts at Weston hospital.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;At University Hospitals Bristol &amp; Weston NHS Foundation Trust we want to recruit a large number of Domestic Assistants to our Temporary Staffing Bureau to create a bank of temporary workers who are keen to work flexibly in various assignments across Weston.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your day to day duties will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;General cleaning Duties within designated areas, including cleaning of toilets and bathrooms on a daily basis. Vacuuming, dusting, cleaning of surfaces and mopping of floors to the standard stated in the cleaning specification for the area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The cleaning of beds and re-making with clean linen&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collect clinical and non-clinical waste and dirty linen and take it to the designated collection point&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Receipt and regeneration of cook-chill food according to specification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The distribution of meals to patients, with attention given to the Presentation of the meals in an attractive manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a flexible approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have good reading and writing plus numeric skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be self-motivated and friendly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a strong attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In reward for your hard work you will benefit from:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free provision of uniform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible working hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to a multitude of discounts in local and national outlets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;bankrecruitment@uhbristol.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
